Block.Name: Robot 1 Dynamics
Block.P:
Set the robot stamina to a value between 0.1 and 1. Note that a higher value of stamina corresponds to more battery power which inversely impacts the mass of the robot. This will reduce its agility.
Likewise, higher values of accuracy will come at a cost of higher rates of discharge for the battery pack.
Choose values carefully to reflect these tradeoffs.
